de">{{Cite web|title=UN Comtrade Database|url=https://comtrade.un.org/data/|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220328082545/https://comtrade.un.org/data/|dead-url=no}} Database search on HS Code 70 "Glass and glassware", Trading partner "Turkmenistan", Reporters "All"</ref>

